Classes
Class
Description
CourseDBElement
Data Element class that implements Comparable interface It consists of five attributes: the Course ID (String), the CRN (int), the number of credits (int), the room number (String), and the instructor name (String).
CourseDBManager
Data Manager Class that implements CourseDBManagerInterface This class allows the user to read input from a file or from the textfields and add it to the data structure through its add method.
CourseDBStructure
Data Structure Class that implements CourseDBStructureInterface This class implements an hash table with buckets.
